<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi>h</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
1|prec|h_{max}
